  "text": "This stage aims to clarify what is the best solution among different topologies based on the computational theory of the ANN. To achieve that, a comparative study will be performed to ensure the best ANN alternative for this concrete domain. The alternatives that have been included for this stage are listed in Table 3 . Jordan-Elman Networks ELN These are dynamic neural networks which have connections from their hidden layer back to a special copy layer [CITATION_1] ",
